            "detailed_description": "<p><b>Starseed Pilgrim is a game about tending a symphonic garden, exploring space, and embracing fate.</b>\n</p>\n\n<p>You are a gardener, tending to empty noise and empty space to fill them both with colour.<br>\nYou are a refugee, building your own world away from the spreading darkness.<br>\nYou are an explorer, discovering new places, new rules, and new fascinations.\n</p>\n\n<p><b>The Universe Is Bigger Than You Know.</b><p>\n",
